000090 REMARKS.                    THIS PROGRAM READS UP TO 40
000100                             CHARACTERS FROM A 'PARM' STATEMENT
000110                             IN AN 'EXEC' CARD, AND DISPLAYS THE
000120                             INFORMATION OBTAINED UPON THE
000130                             SYSTEM CONSOLE.
000140
000150 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
000160
000170 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
000180
000190 SOURCE-COMPUTER.                 IBM-360.
000200
000210 OBJECT-COMPUTER.                 IBM-360.
000220
000230 DATA DIVISION.
