000350 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
000360
000370     ENTER LINKAGE.
000380     CALL 'GETPAR' USING PARM.
000390     IF          PARM IS EQUAL TO SPACES,
000400         GO TO QUERY.
000410     DISPLAY     SPACE UPON CONSOLE,
000420     DISPLAY     PARM UPON CONSOLE,
000430     DISPLAY     SPACE UPON CONSOLE.
000440 QUERY.
000450     DISPLAY '**        **   DO YOU WISH TO CONTINUE ?'
000460         UPON CONSOLE.
000470 ASK.
000480     DISPLAY '**        **   REPLY Y OR N' UPON CONSOLE.
000490     ACCEPT ANSWER FROM CONSOLE.
000500     IF ANSWER IS EQUAL TO 'Y' GO TO FINISH.
000510     IF ANSWER IS NOT EQUAL TO 'N' GO TO ASK.
000520     ENTER LINKAGE.
000530     CALL 'COBDUM' USING SIXTEEN.
000540     ENTER COBOL.
000550 FINISH.
000560     STOP RUN.
